snippet.title: Fish Game Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
FREE Demo Coming to Steam Next Fest October 9, 2023! Wishlist now for a reminder! Coming to Early Access shortly after! https://shorturl.at/lpNZ5

Fish Game is a home aquarium sim from A Shell in the Pit, Smarter Every Day and Creative Ink Games. Easily create beautiful tanks with simulated plant growth and water chemistry. Watch your pets grow, interact and thrive (or not!) with their tankmates. Manicure your plants (even replant your clippings!), build stunning aquascapes and gardens. Enjoy gorgeous, living aquariums on any screen in your home.
